---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Whisk Bake Repeat">
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-amber-50 px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-rose-700">
            About
          </p>

          <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-stone-950 md:text-6xl">
            The story behind Whisk Bake Repeat
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-6 text-base leading-8 text-stone-700 md:text-lg">
            Whisk Bake Repeat is a home baking business built around custom
            cakes, sweet treats, and the joy of making celebrations feel a
            little more personal.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-rose-50 p-4 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-rose-100">
          <img
            src="/images/about-me.JPG"
            alt="The baker behind Whisk Bake Repeat"
            class="aspect-[4/5] w-full rounded-[1.5rem] object-cover object-center"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-3xl space-y-6 text-base leading-8 text-stone-700 md:text-lg">
  <p class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-stone-950">
    Welcome to Whisk Bake Repeat!
  </p>

  <p>
    I’m a mom to two sweet boys, a wife, and currently back in school working
    toward my certificate to become an ODS-C. Life stays pretty full, but my
    heart has always been in baking.
  </p>

  <p>
    For as long as I can remember, I’ve loved being in the kitchen—cooking,
    baking, experimenting, and bringing ideas to life. I’m usually the family
    member showing up with the cake, and I wouldn’t have it any other way!
  </p>

  <p>
    Whisk Bake Repeat is the result of a long-time dream to turn that passion
    into something I can share with others. I love creating custom cakes and
    sweet treats, especially when I can take inspiration from trends or ideas
    and put my own creative twist on them.
  </p>

  <p>
    A little more about me—I love reading, doing jigsaw puzzles, taking walks
    with my little family, playing board games with my siblings &#40;things get
    competitive!&#41;, and relaxing with a good drama or crime show.
  </p>

  <p>
    Thank you so much for being here. If you’re looking for custom cakes or
    sweet treats to help make your event extra special—and a little less
    stressful—I’d love to be part of it. Don’t hesitate to reach out!
  </p>

  <div class="pt-2 font-serif text-xl font-semibold leading-7 text-stone-950">
    <p>Autumn</p>
    <p>Whisk Bake Repeat</p>
    <p class="text-rose-700">Baking Life’s Sweetest Moments</p>
  </div>

  <div class="pt-4">
    <a
      href="/#contact"
      class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-rose-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-rose-800"
    >
      Ask About Availability
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>